Package edu.uidaho.junicon.runtime.util

Provides common utilities for logging and file copying.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ILogger
    Provides logging, debugging, and tracing capabilities common to interpreters.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BatRunner
    Runs a command file given as a string, and waits for it to finish.
    FileCopy
    Provides methods to read and write files to and from strings, and to copy files.
    JarRunner
    Runs the main-class in the given jar file's manifest.
    LoggerFactory
    The LoggerFactory class createas a logger to manage error, info, and trace messages.
    ZipExtractor
    Extracts files from a zip archive.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ILogger.Trace  

Package edu.uidaho.junicon.runtime.util Description

Provides common utilities for logging and file copying. Also contains runtime utilities such as JarRunner.
